    <div class="ba-grid" id="tool-7" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#7 · $20–$69/MO · FREE TIER AVAILABLE</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Zapier — Best cross-tool workflow automation</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For businesses that need to connect disparate tools and automate hand-offs between them without a developer.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Zapier is the automation glue. It doesn't do marketing itself — it connects the tools that do. A new form submission triggers a CRM entry, an email sequence, and a Slack alert. A new blog post triggers a social post and an email notification. If you have 5+ tools in your stack and they don't talk to each other, Zapier saves significant manual work.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>6,000+ app integrations — connects almost any combination of tools</h4><p>If you can name two tools, there's almost certainly a Zapier integration between them.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Multi-step Zaps let you build complex cross-tool workflows without code</h4><p>New CRM contact → welcome email → Slack alert → add to Google Sheet. All automated.</p></div></li>
