        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#8 · $29–$99/MO · PAID ONLY</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">CoSchedule — Best marketing calendar and content scheduling</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For small marketing teams that need a shared editorial calendar to coordinate blog, social, and email campaigns.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">CoSchedule is the editorial calendar tool of record. It's built for teams that are coordinating blog publishing, social promotion, email campaigns, and PR outreach in one visual calendar. The ReQueue feature automatically repurposes high-performing social posts to fill scheduling gaps. Good for a 2–5 person marketing team. Overkill for a solo operator.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
