          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>ReQueue auto-fills social gaps with evergreen content reschedules</h4><p>A set-and-semi-forget approach to keeping social channels active.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Headline Analyzer tool is genuinely useful for blog writers</h4><p>Rates your headline for SEO, emotion, and power word density before you publish.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: designed for teams with existing content, not for creating it</h4><p>CoSchedule organizes your content. It doesn't write, optimize, or rank it. You need a content creation layer underneath it.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

